cu.explanation_en: Setting the gNB ID to an invalid hexadecimal format will cause ID parsing errors during gNB initialization, leading to startup failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting the gNB ID to an invalid hexadecimal format will cause ID parsing errors during gNB initialization, leading to startup failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB ID 設定為無效的十六進位格式將導致 gNB 初始化期間的 ID 解析錯誤，導致啟動失敗。
